data.description: Recently updated 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home conveniently located by OBU, Dean Weigant Park, St. Anthony hospital, and with easy access to Highway 177. Interior features include stainless steal appliances, luxury vinyl flooring throughout, and updated kitchen and bath. Exterior features include fenced yard and roof replaced in 2021. Call for your private showing today! (Home has central heat and air-AC was recently repaired).
